title: Qui dansera avec les stars ?
overview: Each season, new dancers join the troupe of professional dancers of Danse avec les stars. But before setting foot on the floor of the most famous dance hall in France, you have to pass high-level auditions. And for the second consecutive season, these were filmed! This year, there are 34 dancers who have the same dream and to make it come true, they will experience strong, intense and sometimes difficult moments... Find out who will be the new professional dancer (or dancer) who will join the big DALS family this season.
